  \page vitelotte_user_manual_diffusion_images_page Diffusion images

  Diffusion images are image produced by diffusing colors defined on curves and points thorough the domain. It offers a simple way to create and edit images with few textures but complex colors gradients.

  Diffusing colors from some constraints is the same as finding a function that interpolates these constraints. There is obviously several ways to do this. We will discuss two of them here: harmonic and bi-harmonic interpolation.

